 up from the floor. He palpated with translucent fingers the dwarf’s round forehead and added, “I told you not to butt in. Now you got it. A dwarf woman is what you need.”

Fred, his eyes bulging, said nothing.

“You’ll sleep at my place tonight,” decided Shock, and carried the Potato Elf toward the exit.





